IMAPAccount Emma
Host mail.cock.li
Port 993
User eemmaa@waifu.club
PassCmd "pass mail.cock.li/eemmaa@waifu.club"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore Emma-remote
Account Emma

MaildirStore Emma-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/Emma/
Inbox ~/Mail/Emma/Inbox
Trash ~/Mail/Emma/Trash

Channel Emma
Far :Emma-remote:
Near :Emma-local:
Patterns INBOX "Sent Items" Drafts Trash Spam?
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
